c0 sc0 ls0 ws0">当然，<span class="_ _d"></span>我也理解你的顾虑。<span class="_ _d"></span>一般来说，<span class="_ _d"></span>人在年轻的时候，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc3 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">思想比较活跃，<span class="_ _6"></span>不肯就范于任何一种认识；<span class="_ _6"></span>而所谓的<span class="_ _6"></span>“批判</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc0 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls24 ws0">思考”<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls1e">，也让很多人在接触经典时<span class="ls1f">，因为担心失去自己的立</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc1 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">场，<span class="_ _6"></span>宁肯采取远离的态度，<span class="_ _a"></span>敬而远之。<span class="_ _6"></span>然而，<span class="_ _a"></span>人到了垂暮之</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc2 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">际，<span class="_ _5"></span>在感受到悲欢离合的种种经历、<span class="_ _5"></span>饱尝了生老病死的无常</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
